<div class="wrap glossary-shell">
  <aside class="aside">
    <div class="aside-label">Term groups</div>
    <p>Definitions organized by how they apply to behavioral diagnosis and marketing strategy.</p>
    <ol class="toc">
      <li><a href="#beam-terms">BEAM Framework Terms</a></li>
      <li><a href="#behavioral-science">Behavioral Science Terms</a></li>
